HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelScan - Report status, or start or stop a channel scan


usage: HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelScan [-h] --hdhr HDHR [--status | --start | --stop] [--source SOURCE] [--use-cloud-discovery]

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --hdhr HDHR           the HDHomeRun to manage
  --status              status of the channel scan (default action)
  --start               start a channel scan
  --stop, --abort       stop a channel scan
  --source SOURCE       specify a source type
  --use-cloud-discovery
                        use the SiliconDust Cloud API services to discover local tuners



Scenerio:

You want to start a new channel scan

    HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelScan --hdhr=myhdhr.local --start

You want to check the status of an ongoing scan

    HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelScan --hdhr=myhdhr.local --status
